--- 
name   : locat
title  : LOCat
summary: Lines of Code Attache
contact: trans <transfire@gmail.com>
created: 2011-07-07
authors: Thomas Sawyer
license: BSD-2-Clause

description:
  LOCat is a customizable Lines-Of-Code analysis tool.
  LOC might not be the most useful metric in the universe,
  but it still provides useful information and can be
  a lot of fun.

requires:
  - grit
  - ansi
  - detroit (build)
  - qed     (test)

